quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  77,41,Ndithudi anthu angwiro adzakhala mu mthunzi wozizira ndi pa akasupe
  77,42,Ndi zipatso zimene afuna kukhosi kwawo
  77,43,Idyani ndipo imwani mosangalala chifukwa cha zimene mudachita
  77,44,"Ndithudi, mmenemo ndi mmene timalipirira anthu angwiro"
  77,45,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,46,Idyani ndipo musangalale kwa kanthawi kochepa. Ndithudi inu ndinu oipa kwambiri
  77,47,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,48,"Ndipo zikanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: “Weramani.” Iwo amakana kutero"
  77,49,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,50,Kodi ndi Uthenga uti woposa uwu umene adzaukhulupirire